    <section class="home">
        
        <video class="video-slide" src="/video/tiger.mp4" autoplay muted loop></video>
        <div class="content active">
            <h1>Animal World<br><span>Island</span></h1>
            <p>A wonderful place to explore and learn about the diverse and wonderful world of animals. This website provides vivid, fascinating and detailed information about animals, from the smallest species to the giants on earth. Through exploration, this site will inspire you about the importance of protecting and respecting the lives of these amazing creatures.</p>
